d Dallara F314 prior round 8}}-[[Volkswagen]]\n| {{flagicon|MCO}}  [[Charles Leclerc (racing driver)|Charles Leclerc]]\n| 33\n| 4\n| 3\n| 5\n| 13\n| 363.5\n| 4th\n|rowspan=3 style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| '''3rd'''\n|-\n|rowspan=2| Dallara F312-[[Volkswagen]]\n| {{flagicon|IND}} [[Arjun Maini]]\n| 33\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 27\n| 18th\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Alessio Lorandi]]\n| 33\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 26\n| 20th\n|-\n|rowspan=4| [[2016 FIA Formula 3 European Championship|2016]]\n| {{Tooltip|Dallara F316|Used Dallara F312 prior round 7}}-[[Volkswagen]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Callum Ilott]]\n| 30\n| 2\n| 2\n| 3\n| 6\n| 226\n| 6th\n|rowspan=4| 4th\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|Dallara F316|Used Dallara F314 prior round 5}}-[[Volkswagen]]\n| {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Anthoine Hubert]]\n| 30\n| 1\n| 1\n| 1\n| 3\n| 160\n| 8th\n|-\n|rowspan=2| Dallara F316-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Harrison Newey]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 22\n| 18th\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Pedro Piquet]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 19\n| 19th\n|-\n|rowspan=6| [[2017 European Formula 3 Championship|2017]]\n| {{Tooltip|Dallara F312|Used Dallara F316 in the first nine rounds}}-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n| {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Harrison Newey]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 106\n| 11th\n|rowspan=6| 5th\n|-\n| Dallara F316-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Joey Mawson]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 1\n| 83\n| 13th\n|-\n| {{Tooltip|Dallara F316|Used Dallara F312 in the round 3, F317 in the rounds 4-9}}-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Pedro Piquet]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 1\n| 80\n| 14th\n|-\n|rowspan=3| Dallara F317-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n| {{flagicon|DEU}} [[David Beckmann]]\n| 30\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 45\n| 16th\u2020\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Max Defourny]]\n| 3\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 2\n| 18th\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Felipe Drugovich]]\n| 3\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| N/A\n| NC\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[2018 FIA Formula 3 European Championship|2018]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |Dallara F316-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n|{{Flagicon|RU}} [[Artem Petrov]]\n|30\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|7\n|20th\n| rowspan=\"4\" |5th\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|GER}} [[Sophia Fl\u00f6rsch]]\n|21\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|1\n|22nd\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|DNK}} Frederik Vesti\n|3\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|NC\n|-\n|Dallara F317-[[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes]]\n|{{Flagicon|IRN}} [[Keyvan Andres]]\n|30\n|0\n|0\n|0\n|1\n|18\n|18\n|}\n\u2020Shared results with the other team\n\n==Timeline==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size:85%;\"\n!colspan=2| Current series\n|-\n| [[ADAC Formula 4]]\n| 2015\u20132019\n|-\n| [[Italian Formula 4 Championship]]\n| 2017\u20132019\n|-\n| [[Formula Regional European Championship]]\n| 2019\n|-\n| [[Euroformula Open Championship]]\n| 2020\n|-\n!colspan=2| Former series\n|-\n| [[the Netherlands|Dutch]] and [[Benelux]] [[Formula Ford]]\n| 1975-1996\n|-\n| [[German Formula Three Championship]]\n| 1997\u20132002 2004-2014\n|-\n| [[Formula Renault Northern European Cup|Formula Renault 2.0 Netherlands]]\n| 2003-2005\n|-\n| [[Formula 3 Euro Series]]\n| 2006, 2012\n|-\n| [[Formula Renault Northern European Cup]]\n| 2006-2012\n|-\n| [[ADAC Formel Masters]]\n| 2008-2009\n|-\n| [[FIA European Formula 3 Championship]]\n| 2012-2018\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.vanamersfoortracing.nl/}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ach|ach}}\n{{succession box|title=[[Italian F4 Championship|Italian F4 Teams' Champion]]|before=[[Prema Powerteam|Prema Theodore Racing]]|after=Incumbent|years=[[2019 Italian F4 Championship|2019]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n[[Category:Dutch auto racing teams]]\n[[Category:Formula Renault teams]]\n[[Category:Formula Renault Eurocup teams]]\n[[Category:Formula 3 Euro Series teams]]\n[[Category:FIA Formula 3 European Championship teams]]\n[[Category:British Formula Three teams]]\n[[Category:German Formula 